Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:05.30,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Junji and Asako's{\i0}\N{\i1}Know-Your-Simoun Lecture{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.73,0:00:03.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Jun-Jun and Asa-Asa's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.20,0:00:06.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,...Radio Wave Illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.31,0:00:13.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,We began with a title not discussed in\Nthe meeting. It's the Simoun lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.58,0:00:14.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Part one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.02,0:00:17.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is the director...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:17.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,The director, Nishimura...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.02,0:00:19.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Junji-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.95,0:00:23.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I'm Asako Nishida,\Nthe character designer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:26.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,I also serve as animation supervisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.66,0:00:30.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,And also light comic relief...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:34.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but right now, I'm in\Ncharge of Wauf love. And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:40.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,The conductor of love who conveys\NWauf's allure to all our viewers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.28,0:00:45.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,This has nothing to do\Nwith what's on screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.01,0:00:49.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, if you see\Nthe Messis, you think of Wauf...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.32,0:00:51.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,I came up with Wauf's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.35,0:00:53.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh? What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.29,0:00:57.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, basically, all male names\Nare supposed to end with an F...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:01:00.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,That was one of\Nthe rules, as you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.49,0:01:01.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,So "Wau"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.63,0:01:03.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, to be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.10,0:01:08.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Since Wauf's a minor character,\NI thought a short name would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:10.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,You mean {\i1}that{\i0} was your reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:12.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.94,0:01:17.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,I looked it up in a Latin dictionary,\Nwondering if it had some meaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.94,0:01:20.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Actually, in the case of the Messis...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.95,0:01:23.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,...it means grain or something similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.75,0:01:28.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,As for "Wauf," I just decided\Non it by the way it sounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.25,0:01:31.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Like the sound you make\Nwhen you're kissing... Wauf!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.82,0:01:37.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Like, "What's with that?" Anyway, we'll\Ngo back to the topic of Wauf later...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.23,0:01:39.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,At this point...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.36,0:01:43.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,...was this where\NNeviril's love affair begins?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.77,0:01:50.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes. Needless to say,\Naround episodes seven and eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:57.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,...Neviril actually begins to have\Nfeelings to some degree forAer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:02:01.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,That was my intention for\Nthis part. The thing is, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.86,0:02:03.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Seven and eight?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.42,0:02:07.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,When she said pair...\N"You are my pair." That was when...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.86,0:02:10.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Actually, she said, "I am your pair!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:11.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:15.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:17.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,"I am your pair."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.70,0:02:23.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,I tried to convey how she didn't\Nrealize her feelings at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.38,0:02:28.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,And after that, it was a matter\Nof figuring out how to make Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.82,0:02:32.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,...realize that she\Nwas in love with Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.52,0:02:37.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,That was the story arc\NI wanted to build.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:42.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aerjust thought she\Nshould follow Floe's words.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:46.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just kissing her if there was\Na Ri M_a_jon she'd like to invent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.20,0:02:47.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thinking like a child, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.03,0:02:51.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Since Aer has no complex\Nemotions like Neviril does...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:59.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,But anyway, we shouldn't be\Ntalking about stuff so far ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.01,0:03:04.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait. She's now like, "What\Ngood will it do to lose all hope?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.15,0:03:05.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,I assumed...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:10.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,...she was implying that she'd already\Nseen her share of hopelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.86,0:03:14.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.56,0:03:14.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:18.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,You once asked me, "Just what\Ndid Aer go through before all this?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.10,0:03:21.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.93,0:03:21.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:27.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's probably seen more than\Nanyone should in a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:29.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Like in episode four...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:32.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,...she's done things like\Nhacking a soldierto pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.05,0:03:38.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's been in an environment\Nmore harsh than one should be in?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:39.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:40.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:47.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,So she's only seen\Nthe negative aspects of this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:51.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Negative aspects?\NI don't know if you'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:54.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not about pluses or minuses...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.37,0:03:59.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's simply that she knows that there\Nare harsh environments like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:06.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,So it's not like she's known hardship\Nand wants to go to a better place...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:09.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's more that she's\Naware and can remain calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.88,0:04:13.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's the nuance I was going for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.66,0:04:21.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,I really want to draw that Aer who's\Nso gung-ho about going into battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.89,0:04:25.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Very well.\NThat will come up next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.40,0:04:26.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:29.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,You mean in episode 27?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:36.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,In that sense,\Nseeing Aer in a scene like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.31,0:04:40.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,I mean Neviril...\NAnd Paraietta's relationship...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:44.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can see that it's\Na little... How should I say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:49.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,It seems more like they're playing\Nhouse. It's that nuance that I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:55.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,You mean it still hasn't\Nevolved into a true romance?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:57.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Like two kids pretending.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:05:00.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're pretty much\Nhitting it on the nose there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:05.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I felt that we should\Nkeep it that way between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:08.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,These scenes here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:10.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Afterthe first approval...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.78,0:05:15.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,...we were told, "Make Domin_u_ra\Nmore drop-dead gorgeous!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.45,0:05:19.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,That was a direct request from\Nthe director. You left me a little note.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.72,0:05:21.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,And you complied?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:27.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Domin_u_ra's character... At what point\Ndid you really start getting into...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:30.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,...or should I say\Nfocusing more on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:36.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Domin_u_ra? Well, what can I say...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.97,0:05:41.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,In the end, it's really Domin_u_ra\Nwho's most like an outsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:45.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um... A-Aer, on the other hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:50.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,...came from outside, began shaking\Nthings up, and {\i1}is{\i0} a sort of heretic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:54.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,But Aer herself doesn't have\Na problem with that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:57.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,But that's not\Nthe case with Domin_u_ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.89,0:06:00.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,She knows that she's an outsider...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:05.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and you can see that it's causing\Nher distress. That's my take.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:11.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,But she also knows she can only go\Nso far and is resigned to that fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:14.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's the kind of person she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:18.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,And that's the kind of mind-set\NI had myself when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.18,0:06:20.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:22.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can relate to her kind of character.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:25.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,You felt isolated, you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.62,0:06:28.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, I wouldn't say isolated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:32.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,So you had those drills\Nhanging from your head too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:34.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just like her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.19,0:06:36.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,The bamboo curls!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.13,0:06:38.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's something\Nfrom my secret past.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:41.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,I went through that for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:49.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,The background music in\Nthis scene is pretty interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:55.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right, it really stands out like a sore\Nthumb on the CD! At least to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:59.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because the other\Nsongs are tango-esque, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:04.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then this mechanical-sounding\Nbackground music is suddenly heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:08.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,I knew it would be\Na challenge, but it fit like a glove.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:09.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Whoa... goosebumps!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.86,0:07:16.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,So in your eyes,\NWauf was just a minor character?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.67,0:07:18.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:21.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, time out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:24.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Wauf.\NWe'll get back to you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:26.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,This kiss here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:27.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.91,0:07:31.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is shejust repeating\Nwhat Aer told her...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:33.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,...or was she being mischievous?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.75,0:07:38.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, she's truly acting on it in\Nall seriousness... The way a child will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:43.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,So she's just a really pure-minded\Ncharacter. No motives at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:49.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,In the beginning, Rimone was always\Ntrying to shun Domin_u_ra, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:54.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,But now she's attracted to her...\NDid she sense her motherly instinct?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:59.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Or did she see her as a person trying\Nto achieve perfection in one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:03.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and that was what drew her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.22,0:08:06.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Forgive me...\NI really don't understand Rimone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:08.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're copping out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:12.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Jun-Jun totally copped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.79,0:08:16.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,R-Rimone's the one\NI can relate to the least!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.13,0:08:20.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,You've alienated every last Rimone\Nfan in Japan, all across the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.97,0:08:22.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:26.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Watching the show,\Nyou may think that about her...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.74,0:08:30.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but for me, Rimone is something\NI have to handle with kid gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:34.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Something about her keeps\Nme from answering promptly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:38.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you're too invested,\Nyou'd be committing a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:40.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,So you're using restraint?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.75,0:08:44.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm just saying I don't\Nunderstand her as a character!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:49.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,But doesn't that make\Nyou want to know her all the more?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.30,0:08:55.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,In that sense, the whole issue\Nis a pretty scary one for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.54,0:08:58.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'd be scared to try to figure her out...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:09:04.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's a "No offense, but I don't\Nthink I'll touch you" kind of character.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:09.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,So all your excess passion\Nis channeled into Domin_u_ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:12.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Into the bamboo curls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.85,0:09:15.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think that's\Nwhat happened, more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:20.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,But these two... Of course\Nwhen we first started out...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:25.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,...we never intended for\Nthem to go into this direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.36,0:09:29.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's more like they headed\Ndown that path on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:30.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Pretty much...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:37.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here, she's talking about\Nthe fact that she's an immigrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:40.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,You told me this over drinks last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:47.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,What it means to be an immigrant...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.72,0:09:52.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Whether it means you're from\Nanother country or another planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:55.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,You mean that discussion we had.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.93,0:10:03.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,The geography we're talking about...\NIn a historical sense, as well as...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:07.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess I should\Nsay a physical sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:11.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can think of it as\Nencompassing all of outer space.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.78,0:10:16.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,I do believe that, but in\Nthe 26-episode Simoun worldview...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.68,0:10:23.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,...there's no need for viewers\Nto expand their perception that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:29.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,And if it were, we'd be opening a can\Nof worms without resolving a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:33.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,And we still haven't\Nresolved anything to this day...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.37,0:10:34.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,You said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.60,0:10:36.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think that would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:41.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,But my imagined world has space\Nand immigrants from other planets.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:44.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's the kind of worldview\NI'm hoping to create.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.81,0:10:48.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Matsuda-san, use space engine\Nbackground music right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:54.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.19,0:10:59.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right here in this scene is\Nprecisely where we see Domin_u_ra...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.99,0:11:02.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,The birth of "Drill-nura"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:07.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Drill-nura is born! That's what I was\Nthinking when we did this scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:14.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,In the first draft of the script, you\Nsee her coming barefoot towards us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.91,0:11:18.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,And right after that,\Nshe's stuffing herself with food.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:23.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, so making her only wearthat slip\Nin those scenes was your doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:28.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,More or less. So we had the script,\Ncharacter design, and costumes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:32.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and it seemed she\Nkept sliding towards drilldom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:36.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,I get a strong sense of that\Nin this episode's second half.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:42.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,When you see her stroking\NRimone's cheek in this scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:45.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the segment director said,\N"Try to make it look like it feels good."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:48.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,"You know, like it's a crime!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:53.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was like, "Gotcha!"\NThat's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:55.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wasn't consulted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:58.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?\NI was totally gung-ho about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.62,0:12:02.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I made it look as criminal\Nas possible. At least in my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:06.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Pretty criminal right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:14.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everything's spiraling out of control\Nwithout the director's knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.37,0:12:17.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Itjust keeps snowballing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:22.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:26.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,As far as what happens when\Nyou do the Emerald Ri M_a_jon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:31.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,At this point in the story,\Ndoes Domin_u_ra herself know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:32.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:35.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,She may know\Nthat it's one possibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.96,0:12:41.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but basically, all she's sure of is\Nthat she won't know unless she tries.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:47.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're surrounded by enemies,\Nand it's a matter of life or death...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:52.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just what is her motivation\Nfor doing the Emerald Ri M_a_jon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:55.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Does she think\Nthey can change the tide?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.31,0:13:00.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, she has a more...\NIt's a very personal reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.25,0:13:07.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,She knows that this battle\Nmeans nothing to them anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:13.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,They'll get killed if she doesn't do\Nsomething now, so it's now or never?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:19.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, um, we'll continue\Nthis discussion later. I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.03,0:13:21.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:25.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.97,0:13:31.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,W-We're ending on this doll?\NRoatreamon's doll will close it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:35.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um, as far as\Nthe Emerald Ri M_a_jon is concerned...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.38,0:13:39.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,...we still have an immense\Namount of explaining to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:42.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,How should I say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:48.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,The fact that they did\Nthe Emerald Ri M_a_jon here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.63,0:13:53.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,...was a huge catalyst that moved\Nthis story towards its conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:58.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,And we really do need to talk\Nabout the structure of this arc.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.80,0:14:02.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, I mean\NDomin_u_ra's emotional state!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.31,0:14:04.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's what you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.84,0:14:07.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,About Domin_u_ra's emotional state...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:13.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,The moment she drew herself up\Nto her full height in that scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.49,0:14:24.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,She'd made up her mind totally to live\Nthe rest of her life with Rimone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:29.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,So in my eyes, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.90,0:14:33.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,What happened\Nhere gave her greatjoy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.31,0:14:39.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,And so at this time, even if they didn't\Nthink at all of their comrades...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.64,0:14:43.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I thought it was perfectly all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.12,0:14:48.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Old Lady Bamboo Curls snatched\NRimone and skipped town!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:52.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do something about that please!
